name: HepatitisBVirusInfectionTestsForHepatitisBVirusNucleicAcid
title: Hepatitis B Virus Infection (Tests for hepatitis B virus Nucleic Acid)
purpose:
(Clinical Focus: This set of values contains codes for laboratory test names associated with detecting the presence of Hepatitis B virus DNA),(Data Element Scope: Laboratory tests names that were ordered or observed.),(Inclusion Criteria: component: Hepatitis B virus DNA;
Hepatitis B virus polymerase DNA),(Exclusion Criteria: None)
